author: Swagata Dam
title: Shaheen Bhatt’s Birthday Wish For Sister Alia Bhatt Is Too Sweet!
text:
Bollywood’s li’l Miss Sunshine Alia Bhatt turns 24 today. And on the occasion of her birthday, her sister Shaheen Bhaat shared an adorable #sisterselfie along with the cutest caption. The duo recently moved out of their parents’ house and now stay together in a brand new swanky apartment. Check this out. A post shared by Shaheen Bhatt (@shaheenb) on Mar 15, 2017 at 4:17am PDT 
Isn’t this so sweet? Happy birthday, Alia! 2
